  <acronym>ALLOPULM</acronym>
  <official_title>Prospective Cohort Study of Late Pulmonary Complications in Patients Who Received Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cells Transplantation: Estimation of Incidence and Identification of Distinct Nosologic Entities</official_title>
